02:20:54,001 --> 02:20:56,936
Uangku ada di kantor itu, benar?

1849
02:20:59,339 --> 02:21:02,308
Kalau dia mencoba memberikanku alasan omong kosong di sana...

1850
02:21:02,376 --> 02:21:04,640
