1862
02:21:54,161 --> 02:21:56,595
Sebaiknya begitu, bajingan.

1863
02:21:58,332 --> 02:22:00,300
Baiklah.

1864
02:22:00,367 --> 02:22:02,801
Ayo pergi.

1865
02:22:15,248 --> 02:22:17,239
Kau punya kuncinya, ya kan?

1866
02:22:20,053 --> 02:22:24,353
Baiklah, sekarang, saat kita masuk ke sana,
